name: Stop Shiling!!
description: Welcome back! Shill "shill refers to someone who purposely gives onlookers, participants or  "marks" the impression of an enthusiastic customer independent of the seller" Stop shilling your work to every tweet out there. Have some respect for yourself and your work. This does not mean DO not promote your work, but work with other artist or actual fans of your work instead of these shill bots. They are only looking for gains, gains in twitter traction and followers. We are the 1s and 0s and I am 101! Share if you agree!
